    "body": "We agree that variants should be all lower-case.  If package authors want to make multi-word variant names, should they use underscores (eg: `build-type`) or dashes (eg: `build_type`)?  Note that we already use dashes for package names.\r\n\r\nI'm voting for dashes because that's already used for package names.\r\n\r\n",
